From 1850c7eda6b992e2604ff1e6389454023c6e10ca Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sun, 16 Nov 2025 19:55:41 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 01/12] Add Excalidraw map integration to Quartz

This commit adds support for rendering Excalidraw maps in Quartz:

- Add @excalidraw/excalidraw dependency with React compat layer
- Create ExcalidrawTransformer to parse .excalidraw.md files
- Create ExcalidrawMap component for rendering maps
- Integrate transformer and component into Quartz config
- Add conditional rendering in layout for Excalidraw maps

Features:
- Parse Excalidraw drawings from markdown files
- Render maps with SVG preview
- Display marker and zone statistics
- Support for wiki-links in map elements
- Responsive design with mobile support

The Excalidraw plugin is available in obsidian-excalidraw-plugin/
folder with documentation in MAP_FEATURES.md

Related: Add map drawing feature for D&D wiki
